{"name":"About Adventure Companion","permission":{"default":0,"1SlcqeQ3LtMsOcxL":3},"flags":{},"content":"<div>\n<h1>3.5e Adventure Companion - Sunless Citadel</h1>\n<div><strong>3.5e Adventure Companion - Sunless Citadel is unofficial Fan Content permitted under the Fan Content Policy. Not approved/endorsed by Wizards. Portions of the materials used are property of Wizards of the Coast. &copy;Wizards of the Coast LLC.</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"modules/d35e-sunless-citadel/images/sc_cover.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"381\" /></div>\n<div><br />\n<div><em>This is only an adventure companion and it contains only Maps and Foundry implementations of Monsters/Items - no story elements are included. To play Sunless Citadel adventure you will need official Sunless Citadel book. <a href=\"https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/3727/The-Sunless-Citadel-3e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">You can purchase PDF on DriveThruRPG</a></em></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<h2>Welcome to 3.5e Adventure Companion for Sunless Citadel</h2>\n<p>This companion is designed to help you easily run one of the Classic adventures for 3.5 edition of Dungeons &amp; Dragons. With ready to be used maps filled with monsters that are waiting for adventurers, items that you can give to party and traps ready to be sprung, this companion will allow you to focus on the adventure - not the preparation stuff.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Image used in this description is used according to Fan Content Policy.</em></p>\n</div>","_id":"9N522aL5v0EfxaoG"}
